name: Aloms Bar and Restaurant

reviews.review_text: Bad service this is third time that have found hair in my food had ordered an veg soup found a piece of chicken even after showing them the proof staff says it’s cabbage doesn’t know how to speak to the customers very rude. Very bad experience no cleanliness plate an spoons were dirty
Loved their cosy vibes. The food was served hot and was truly delicious. If you need some yummy food during late hours in Margao, this is could be your saviour!

Aloms has been a go to place for late night food cravings.  The food quality hasnt changed much over the years.
Their chinese dishes are always worth having there.

They do have separate section for serving alcohol. Pricing is decent.

description:
# Dining Experience at Aloms Bar and Restaurant, Goa

Nestled in the vibrant heart of Goa, Aloms Bar and Restaurant boasts a commendable rating of 3.8 from a diverse crowd of 1,175 reviewers. Renowned for its late-night indulgences, Aloms captures the culinary essence of "Chinese food" and "dinner," frequently appearing in customer feedback. While the restaurant celebrates its highs in food quality and quantity—both valued by patrons—it grapples with service inconsistencies that recent guests have noted.

## Ambiance & Design

Aloms Bar and Restaurant invites diners in with its cozy, laid-back atmosphere, as captured in various customer photos. The décor features warm lighting that creates a welcoming environment, perfect for those seeking a relaxed dining experience late at night. The restaurant has a designated alcohol section, which adds to the casual bar vibe, making it an ideal spot for unwinding after a long day. The images showcased reveal comfortable seating arrangements that enhance the intimate feel of the establishment, though hints of wear and tear in the furnishings might suggest the need for updates.

## Menu & Culinary Experience

The menu at Aloms presents a delightful array of options, heavily leaning towards tempting Chinese dishes that keep regulars coming back. Guests have sung praises for the flavor and presentation of the food, with many highlighting that the dishes are served hot and delicious. Choices range from hearty noodles to intricate stir-fries, catering to a range of palates. Although the establishment also offers vegetarian options, some reviews caution about the attention to cleanliness, as one customer experienced finding hair in their food, which detracted from an otherwise enjoyable meal.

## Customer Experience & Service

A mixed bag of experiences characterizes the service at Aloms. While some guests appreciate the attentive nature of the staff, others have reported significant issues with rudeness and hygiene. One customer expressed frustration over uncooperative service after finding a piece of chicken in a vegetarian dish, further noting that cleanliness of utensils was not up to standard. However, the restaurant still gathers a loyal following for its late-night offerings, with many appreciating the decent pricing and quality of the food.

## Popularity & Reviews

The sentiment surrounding Aloms is quite varied. It thrives as a beloved haunt for late-night diners in Margao but struggles with maintaining consistency in service standards. Social media and word-of-mouth recommendations underline the restaurant's appeal among locals and tourists regardless of the setbacks. Regular diners maintain that, despite the occasional mishap, the food quality remains a stronghold, making it a reliable pit stop for midnight cravings.

## Utilizing Visual Content

The visual content provided amplifies the narrative of Aloms. Photos reveal inviting plates of steaming dishes, showcasing vibrant colors and enticing presentations that are hard to resist. The cozy ambiance captured in the images reinforces the restaurant's reputation as a go-to locale for late-night food. However, glimpses of untidy spots also note areas needing attention, hinting toward the necessity for improved cleanliness practices which could enhance the overall dining experience.

In summary, Aloms Bar and Restaurant presents an intriguing dining experience: a fascinating blend of delightful Chinese cuisine and a relaxed vibe, marred slightly by service shortcomings and cleanliness concerns. It's a place where food lovers can fulfill their late-night cravings, though potential guests are encouraged to manage expectations regarding service for a truly enjoyable outing.
